snippet.title: The Demon Lord's Daughter and the Tower of Seals - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
In the wake of the Demon Lord's defeat, his daughter, Lilina, finds herself leading a miserable existence without any of the comforts of the castle she once called home. Now she has to make an honest living while seeking out fabled talismans in an attempt to regain her lost powers!

The Demon Lord's Daughter and the Tower of Seals on Kagura Games Store: https://www.kaguragames.com/product/the-demon-lords-daughter-and-the-tower-of-seals/
